author: News Zombie
title: Sword Art Online: Lost Song multiplayer highlighted in trailer, shots
text:
A new trailer and batch of screenshots have been released for Sword Art Online: Lost Song. The media set focuses on the game’s online multiplayer mode and showcases character customization, four-player co-op, and four-on-four team Battle Arena. 
Sword Art Online: Lost Song is scheduled to launch on November 17 for PS4 and PS Vita. 
–
